      <p class="text-lg mb-6 opacity-90">Transcribing data from a cost manual into a spreadsheet introduces catastrophic decimal errors and VLOOKUP failures. Codify your logic into a digital system and eliminate the human element from repetitive calculations.</p>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn bg-white text-[#2D2442] hover:bg-slate-100 border-none px-8 font-bold">Audit Your Bid Process</a>
