    <h2>Data Decay and Margin Erosion</h2>
    <p>
      Relying on a static book often leads to <strong>Margin Erosion</strong>. Without real-time integration between your estimating department and your Job Costing data, you are bidding in a vacuum. Successful firms in 2025 use custom software to close the loop. When actual costs on the field exceed the estimate, the system flags the variance and updates the bidding library for the next project.
    </p>

    <p>
      Automated systems also allow for the inclusion of a dynamic <strong>Escalation Clause</strong>. Instead of manually calculating inflation risk for a project that won't break ground for six months, the software can run sensitivity analyses and adjust the bid based on current market trends.
    </p>

